，亦應一併繳納上訴審裁判費。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　11　　月　　15　　日\r\n                              書記官  吳琬婷","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/HLEV/111%2c%e8%8a%b1%e7%b0%a1%2c159%2c20221115%2c2/pdf"},"JID":"HLEV,111,花簡,159,20221115,2","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"花簡","JNO":"159","JDATE":"20221115","JTITLE":"侵權行為損害賠償(交通)"}